2.text: The English Day of Gemunu Vidyalaya was held on 21st of October in the school main hall. They had invited the Zonal Director of Education as the Chief Guest. After the tradition of lighting the oil lamp, the programme started with the theme song of English Day. It was sung by a group of grade 8 students. The programme consisted of recitals, duets, songs, dances and a play. One of the invited schools presented a group song. In his speech, the principal said that the members of the English Association had worked hard to make the event a success. He also said that he was very proud of his students' talents. Everyone present agreed that it was a well-organized programme.

7.text: One day Nasrudin was taking a traveller across a lake in his boat. While they were talking on various subjects Nasrudin happened to make a minor grammatical mistake.
